<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA95">
<l>pukuntilaṅku mantip poḻutat tariyā</l>
<l>yikaḻnta viraṇiyaṉa tākañ – cukirnteṅkuñ</l>
<l>cintap piḷanta tirumā ṟiruvaṭiyē</l>
<l>vantitteṉ ṉeñcamē vāḻttu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The holy feet of Tirumāl, who as a lion tore up the chest of Hiraṇya</l>
<l>who had scorned [him], so that it got shredded [and] scattered</l>
<l>everywhere at the time that twilight entered [and] glowed,</l>
<l>[these feet] laude [and] praise, my heart.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
